95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:42:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"851a26d569e3eac6c933178dc09bb104fffcaa2f","tid":1571212,"uid":54181,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:45:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54779fe3a2f32de1e5462f601b10e3cb76106b71","tid":1571212,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"851a26d569e3eac6c933178dc09bb104fffcaa2f","tid":1571212,"uid":54181,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:45:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:53:45.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"d01a265bd1469c8ea77ca236acb4f1691f3f8a60","tid":1571212,"uid":306925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:59:12.000Z","msg":"借貴寶地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n1）警察<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">衰野太多，好難一張文宣講晒</span></span></strong><br />\n2）我地前線手足都開始<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反擊得勁D，反擊畫面</span></span></strong>又會被現在好落力打國際戰的<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府拎黎大造文章，條片正好俾外國能更好地體諒我地</span></span></strong><br />\n3）更好利用一些<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">震撼畫面或者橋段，收籠外國人心</span></strong></span><br />\n4）微電影，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇故仔，好多人都會幾OK，有助spread</span></span></strong>我地情況出去<br />\n5）以後我地本地同外國<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣都塞條片的link入去</span></strong></span>，又或者YouTube channel<br />\n<br />\n但廢J我完全不識點樣整呢D片出來，卡通又好真人又好，都唔識，眾籌也沒experience。所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想集結神力，有邊位兄弟覺得有得諗，就幫手spread出去同用力push，小弟廢J P牌仔自push都做唔到</span></span></strong>，sosaad。"},{"pid":"c13b0ed1d5bbbe03f6d80a26fe9d9d8d70f97e74"