幾多升架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"條片有講"},{"pid":"b85e1b9cae4010986141c85d5f25caf5ede620f4","tid":1571212,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:17:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f41f296358659d7ed62b008152fd505a0a1f24c","tid":1571212,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18fa8c938fbf1765d20e73ec023878473f5fcca2","tid":1571212,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea5a85706e1ce5409773143d74a29fe0a68fe354","tid":1571212,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:53:36.000Z","msg":"之前聽唔知邊個油站要身份証登記喎，同埋限買幾多升架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"條片有講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:17:33.000Z","msg":"爬文"},{"pid":"b81c648e91dbac1402d1212170ab38e28ff90fc4","tid":1571212,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a31d8c486ff2377bdf1af2a1872fcab41f21ce02","tid":1571212,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:05:05.000Z","msg":"香港油站有<br />\n中國石油<br />\n中國石化<br />\nEsso <br />\nShell <br />\n加德士<br />\n<br />\n有柴油<br />\n平汽油<br />\n貴汽油<br />\n正常代步車平汽油可以（柴油車引燃<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>用火花，所以得汽油係用係星星之火引燃）<br />\n<br />\n下面三間係香港有車人士常用同有定時平2.4-2.5<br />\n上面2間日日有得平3.5<br />\n下面三間要申請油卡先有優惠。<br />\n油卡通常油站問佢地就會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，資料鳩寫都得（我唔想收廣告短訊同e mail,所以我鳩寫）<br />\n<br />\nEsso通常星期二有平2.5<br />\nShell星期一有平<br />\n加德士就隔個星期六<br />\n<br />\n上面兩間好似日日都有平<br />\n<br />\n最後，如果架車無油要買「外賣」，shell有外賣盒，30蚊個比教「雞」，外賣盒一定要金屬罐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果由其他車油救其他車，去五金鋪同佢講買泵油油喉可以，泵夠油就將條油喉向上拉。<br />\n但有車人士買外賣通常因爲車用完最後的油或者有細船船外機要汽油。<br />\n<br />\n大家要安全使用汽油<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:24:20.000Z","msg":"要否抄身份証?"},{"pid":"f3b11dd195937c2a32e3c1a83f7fd1902f09db5f","tid":1571212,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b81c648e91dbac1402d1212170ab38e28ff90fc4","tid":1571212,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a31d8c486ff2377bdf1af2a1872fcab41f21ce02","tid":1571212,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:05:05.000Z","msg":"香港油站有<br />\n中國石油<br />\n中國石化<br />\nEsso <br />\nShell <br />\n加德士<br />\n<br />\n有柴油<br />\n平汽油<br />\n貴汽油<br />\n正常代步車平汽油可以（柴油車引燃<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>用火花，所以得汽油係用係星星之火引燃）<br />\n<br />\n下面三間係香港有車人士常用同有定時平2.4-2.5<br />\n上面2間日日有得平3.5<br />\n下面三間要申請油卡先有優惠。<br />\n油卡通常油站問佢地就會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，資料鳩寫都得（我唔想收廣告短訊同e mail,所以我鳩寫）<br />\n<br />\nEsso通常星期二有平2.5<br />\nShell星期一有平<br />\n加德士就隔個星期六<br />\n<br />\n上面兩間好似日日都有平<br />\n<br />\n最後，如果架車無油要買「外賣」，shell有外賣盒，30蚊個比教「雞」，外賣盒一定要金屬罐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果由其他車油救其他車，去五金鋪同佢講買泵油油喉可以，泵夠油就將條油喉向上拉。<br />\n但有車人士買外賣通常因爲車用完最後的油或者有細船船外機要汽油。<br />\n<br />\n大家要安全使用汽油<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:24:20.000Z","msg":"要否抄身份証?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:28:23.000Z","msg":"爬文，現時得shell 會外賣，要用信用卡"},{"pid":"10e2035228b5c09f325e01573f7b8bd0bde4c397","tid":1571212,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T18:11:20.000Z","msg":"救車火水泵變得重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce586f987e15f601e8ed9259f819af9e9d663caf","tid":1571212,"uid":105782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a31d8c486ff2377bdf1af2a1872fcab41f21ce02","tid":1571212,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:05:05.000Z","msg":"香港油站有<br />\n中國石油<br />\n中國石化<br />\nEsso <br />\nShell <br />\n加德士<br />\n<br />\n有柴油<br />\n平汽油<br />\n貴汽油<br />\n正常代步車平汽油可以（柴油車引燃<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>用火花，所以得汽油係用係星星之火引燃）<br />\n<br />\n下面三間係香港有車人士常用同有定時平2.4-2.5<br />\n上面2間日日有得平3.5<br />\n下面三間要申請油卡先有優惠。<br />\n油卡通常油站問佢地就會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，資料鳩寫都得（我唔想收廣告短訊同e mail,所以我鳩寫）<br />\n<br />\nEsso通常星期二有平2.5<br />\nShell星期一有平<br />\n加德士就隔個星期六<br />\n<br />\n上面兩間好似日日都有平<br />\n<br />\n最後，如果架車無油要買「外賣」，shell有外賣盒，30蚊個比教「雞」，外賣盒一定要金屬罐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果由其他車油救其他車，去五金鋪同佢講買泵油油喉可以，泵夠油就將條油喉向上拉。<br />\n但有車人士買外賣通常因爲車用完最後的油或者有細船船外機要汽油。<br />\n<br />\n大家要安全使用汽油<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T18:41:58.000Z","msg":"揸tesla冇藉口買外賣油<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />